00:07:21,900 --> 00:07:24,904
...just for taking some pop
diva to and from her concert.

94
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:26,572
- We're one short.
- A singer?

95
00:07:26,738 --> 00:07:29,787
I don't know if you'd call her
a singer. More like a cash cow.

96
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:32,874
Twenty million records sold
already and she's not even 25.

97
00:07:33,036 --> 00:07:34,288
Job's a piece of cake.

98
00:07:34,454 --> 00:07:37,628
We get her there and back. Inside,
they've got their own people.

99
00:07:37,791 --> 00:07:39,919
- Okay.
- Okay. Okay?

100
00:07:40,085 --> 00:07:41,177
- Yeah.
- Like that's it?

101
00:07:41,336 --> 00:07:42,553
Yeah.

102
00:07:42,712 --> 00:07:46,467
- It'll be perfect. Just like old times.
- Better. No one gets killed.

103
00:07:47,217 --> 00:07:50,096
Tomorrow. Good night, guys. See you.

104
00:07:50,261 --> 00:07:53,606
Get in the back, Wendy.
I always get in the back.

105
00:08:21,001 --> 00:08:23,550
Ma'am, if you don't mind,
I suggest you keep moving.

106
00:08:23,712 --> 00:08:25,806
My mother is ma'am, if you don't mind.

107
00:08:29,384 --> 00:08:32,137
- Come on, it's time now. Let's go.
- Okay.

108
00:08:33,555 --> 00:08:36,399
Bernie, Casey, you're out
here. Bry, you're in the room.

109
00:08:36,558 --> 00:08:38,151
Okay.

110
00:08:39,019 --> 00:08:41,989
Let's go, let's go, let's go.

111
00:08:42,147 --> 00:08:44,024
Thank you for coming.

112
00:08:57,787 --> 00:09:00,040
Wow, it was beautiful.

113
00:09:00,623 --> 00:09:03,217
Thanks. What did you
say your name was again?

114
00:09:03,376 --> 00:09:04,969
Mills. Bryan Mills.

115
00:09:05,128 --> 00:09:07,802
- Nice to meet you, Bryan Mills.
- You too.

116
00:09:08,757 --> 00:09:11,886
- You're on. Come on, let's go now.
- Okay, guys.

117
00:09:12,052 --> 00:09:14,350
Excuse me, miss. I know
this isn't the right time.

118
00:09:14,512 --> 00:09:16,355
I have a daughter who
wants to be a singer...

119
00:09:16,514 --> 00:09:18,767
...and was wondering
if you had any tips.

120
00:09:18,933 --> 00:09:20,526
Yeah, I do.

121
00:09:20,685 --> 00:09:22,858
Tell her to pick another career.

122
00:09:25,732 --> 00:09:27,860
I got one. We're waiting
on an air strike...

123
00:09:28,026 --> 00:09:29,778
...and we're waiting and
then my satellite phone rings.

124
00:09:31,237 --> 00:09:32,284
- Who is it?
- Hello?

125
00:09:32,447 --> 00:09:34,245
- The guy we're to terminate.
- Honey.

126
00:09:34,407 --> 00:09:36,250
He'd like to know if we want some tea.

127
00:09:36,409 --> 00:09:37,456
Sorry, guys, it's Kim.

128
00:09:39,329 --> 00:09:41,002
The noise?

129
00:09:41,164 --> 00:09:43,258
I'm at a concert.

130
00:09:43,875 --> 00:09:46,469
You know this song? Yeah?

131
00:09:46,628 --> 00:09:49,802
Yep, that's her. No, no,
no, I'm not attending.

132
00:09:49,964 --> 00:09:51,432
I'm... I'm not attending.

133
00:09:51,591 --> 00:09:54,219
I'm helping some friends
out with security.

134
00:09:54,385 --> 00:09:56,433
Well, of course I met her.

135
00:09:56,596 --> 00:09:58,269
Who do you think's guarding her?

136
00:09:58,431 --> 00:10:00,604
I'm glad you're impressed.

137
00:10:00,767 --> 00:10:03,020
Hey, I'm happy you called.

138
00:10:03,186 --> 00:10:06,440
I'm happy you called. What?

139
00:10:06,606 --> 00:10:08,950
Lunch? Tomorrow?

140
00:10:09,442 --> 00:10:12,742
Sure, sure. I know the place.

141
00:10:12,904 --> 00:10:15,157
Twelve-thirty it is.

142
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:17,287
I'll see you then.

143
00:10:17,826 --> 00:10:19,669
Here he is. And...? What happened?

144
00:10:19,828 --> 00:10:21,671
She wants to have lunch. Okay.

145
00:10:21,830 --> 00:10:24,049
- Just the two of us.
All right. Fantastic.

146
00:10:24,207 --> 00:10:25,959
See? There's progress. That's great.

147
00:10:39,681 --> 00:10:42,901
Who left that gate open? Bry, get
her out of here. Take the lead.

148
00:10:43,059 --> 00:10:44,151
Move! Go, go!

