155
00:11:11,963 --> 00:11:14,261
Come on, come on, drink some more.

156
00:11:23,433 --> 00:11:25,276
It's okay. It's okay. You're safe.

157
00:11:31,149 --> 00:11:32,742
You're safe now.

158
00:11:35,153 --> 00:11:36,405
Bernie.

159
00:11:36,571 --> 00:11:38,539
Casey. Rambo.

160
00:11:39,490 --> 00:11:42,084
Seriously, Bry, you should
think about coming with us.

161
00:11:42,243 --> 00:11:44,837
You've got the edge. There's
more of this to be had.

162
00:11:44,996 --> 00:11:46,919
- She's going to college next year?
- Yep.

163
00:11:47,081 --> 00:11:50,176
- You're gonna lose her.
